<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٨٩٣ - حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5638">مُحَمَّدٌ: </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4092">عَبْدَةُ: </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4195">عُبَيْدُ اللهِ بْنُ عُمَرَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6509">نَافِعٍ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنِ عُمَرَ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> قَالَ: قَالَ رَسُولُ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: <span class="c2">«انْهَكُوا الشَّوَارِبَ وَأَعْفُوا اللِّحَى.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>